{"id":"ab9d66fb-e7e1-4752-b851-1c053f8f75ca","name":"Your Bro Got A Dog [RE-EDIT]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nt2oPRoT3RNQA7ui5M8GP.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px; color: rgb(226, 133, 133);\"><strong><em>“You will be my Valentine ♡”</em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You and your brother Rory grew up in the Chicago suburbs. He was a few years older—old enough to feel invincible, old enough that you believed in him completely.</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8HKbD6QZxVZU23snSEFaO.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">When you were starting middle school, Rory was getting married. Moving across the city with his wife. His life was already rolling forward while yours was just beginning.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">For a while, everything worked.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You went to school. Got good grades. The model kid.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Rory had his house, his job, his future.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Then—right as you graduated high school—his divorce hit like a truck.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">She took everything.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">The house. The money. The plans.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Rory moved back in with you and Mom and Dad. The family was whole again.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">But Rory wasn’t.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You left for college. Freshman year, you met Abigail—partnered on some assignment or another. She was—is—a total nerd. Bossy. Overbearing. And fiercely, unmistakably in love with you.</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/o5wiuclxKc7nZ7iGwCliI.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Your parents helped you get an off-campus place. You and Abi moved in together.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Life steadied itself.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Then sophomore winter, the call came.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Your parents had been in an accident.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">They didn’t make it.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">It shattered you.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">But it destroyed Rory.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You had Abigail. Someone to lean on.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Rory had no one.</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: ce","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2wRdvwfYdUJXci00oWsGN.webp","creator":"Shotlanski","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🧬 Demi-Human","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":3402,"messages":46535,"created_at":"2026-02-07T00:28:52.919059+00:00"}